column5: Any gps mapping available for Lac des Mille Lacs? I presently have Garmin Mapsource Fishing Hotspots but this lake isn't offered under the Ontario unlock code. Does mapping of this lake exist from any other manufacturer?
I'M FROM THUNDER BAY, AND HAVEN'T HEARD OF ANY MAP COVERAGE FOR THE LAKE. IF YOU HEAR OF SOME PLEASE SEND ME AN EMAIL OR MAKE ANOTHER POST. -DAVIS VIEHBECK
Perhaps someone with the Pinpoint GPS could advise? Thanks.
A GPS map of LDML does not exist. Last summer I heard that they are working on one, primarily marking boating hazards.
